### Development Setup

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/mikeckennedy/memberful.git
cd memberful

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows: venv\Scripts\activate

# Install in development mode
uv pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest

# Format code
ruff format

# Run linter
ruff check
```

